reviewText: I know I keep raving about the Magical Scarecrows range, but really it just keeps getting better. Now they have Australian Idol's Cosima De Vito reading one of their magical stories to a bunch of little kids and it's truly, well, MAGICAL!! You just must collect the whole set - search MAGICAL SCARECROWS - AUNTIE LYNN. This video shows Cosima and other celebs with one of the MANY charity aspects to this magical series. Enjoy!!!
